text: Near the residential area, the equipment is very old and the ground is very wet, as if no one has managed it for a long time.  The place is not big, and it's good to come to exercise by the way, but it's really not worth visiting.

Nice park and exercise area; it connects to another exercise area via an approximately 600m track along the Greenway.  Four runs of this makes 2.4km. ☺ Lots of greenery, flora & fauna (well camouflaged- see it?). oh, also some patterned grilles- what do you think those are? 😋

Nice parkway with many joggers, strollers, cyclists, kids, dogs, elderlies. For more than 2 years, It's sad HDB refuses to build a proper and safe access around Queenstown mrt to the walkway, despite many calls in view of safety train and bus commuters.
Nice and quite, just cycle to Bukit Timah rail corridor and back now taking a quite rest here 👍👍👍🙏
